      "writtenOn": "2018-08-27T16:05:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just checking; no change in the physical model snapshot protocol? Can we save a snapshot on an old emulator version and load it safely here, and vice versa? I see you\u0027ve separated into two different state save/loads, but was wondering still.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 806,
