      "writtenOn": "2018-08-27T18:26:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, no change in snapshot protocol.  I renamed the previous save/load for snapshot use only, and the saveState/loadState are for automation.  However, I\u0027m seriously considering merging them, which would break the protocol.  Maybe in a later change :-)",
      "parentUuid": "eae49dd5_f38f8d43",
