        "filename": "android/android-emu/android/virtualscene/SceneCamera.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 98,
      "author": {
        "id": 1233742
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-08-27T18:26:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Nice catch!  I don\u0027t know if it\u0027s possible to get to this point without qemu\u0027s participation, since it requires the camera to be started, but it\u0027s likely that won\u0027t hold true in the future.\n\nI\u0027ll update this to check if the AutomationController is valid first.",
      "parentUuid": "9126a68c_bbdd81f0",
